    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/33900801/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u33900801-32.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/33900801/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">夏十九</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-05-01"
      class="main-meta">2013-05-01 01:38:40</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5910728_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  其实我反而对隋朝比占大部分篇幅的唐要感兴趣，不知为什么作为开国的隋文帝这段看得热血沸腾的，比以前看鲁鲁修的时候还要燃。文献后这个女人也感觉很有意思。陷落在历史里的女人，在唐朝的重要性绝对大得多。就武则天来说，我想不是亲自经历就凭史书还是很难想象一个七旬老妇...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            中国社会科学出版社1990版</span>
                  </div>
